NAME
    Module::Build::SysPath - Module::Build subclass with Sys::Path used in
    new() and ACTION_install()

SYNOPSIS
        use Module::Build::SysPath;
        my $builder = Module::Build::SysPath->new(
            ...

DESCRIPTION
    A subclass of Module::Build.

    See first Sys::Path.

    See Acme::SysPath for example usage.

